    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer it to a clean board and shred it apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Return the<strong> drained potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a small splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mash until smooth</p>",
