    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the<strong> </strong>sauce with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy chicken pie filling</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>creamy chicken pie filling</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and top with the <strong>mash</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your <strong>creamy chicken potato-topped pie</strong></p>",
